CHECK IF INSTALLED WITH
  $ gpio -v

To INSTALL WIRING PI use:
  $ git clone https://github.com/WiringPi/WiringPi.git
  $ cd WiringPi
  $ ./build

NOTES:
  Works as of Apr, 6 2023. Old method stopped working,
  developer stopped maintaining it.
  

To ENABLE I2C use:
  $ sudo raspi-config
    > 3 Interface Options
    > I5 I2C
    > Yes
    > OK
    > Finish (ESC)

Notes:
  After this, if it doesnt immediatly work, give her a sudo reboot.
